high_descs: Turn around, walk straight, then make a right towards the sink.
Get the knife from behind the the sink's faucet.
Turn right and walk towards the table.
Cut the bread into slices.
Turn right and go to the counter next to the sink.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn right and go to the table with the bread.
Get a slice of bread from the table.
Turn left, walk straight, then make a left. Walk straight then right towards the microwave.
Put the bread in the microwave. Turn on the microwave. Take the bread out of the microwave.
Turn around, walk straight, then make a right towards the counter next to the sink.
Put the bread on the counter next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of bread on the counter next to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink and face it.
Pick up the knife laying behind the faucet.
Turn left and walk to the table in front of you.
Use the knife to cut the bread into slices.
Turn around and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the knife near the edge of the counter.
Turn left and walk back to the table with the slices bread.
Pick up a slice of the bread.
Turn left and walk over to the microwave facing it.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave and cook it before taking it back out and closing the door.
Turn left and walk back to the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the slice of cooked bread near the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of sliced bread on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink
Grab the knife that it on top of the sink
Turn left and stop at the white table
Cut the loaf of bread on the table into slices
Turn around and stop at the counter to the left of the sink
Put the knife on the counter
Turn left and go to the white table
Grab one of the slices of bread
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the bread in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and go to the counter to the left of the sink
Put the bread on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting sliced bread on the counter

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the back of the sink.
Turn left and walk forward to face the table.
Cut the bread loaf into slices.
Turn to the right and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn left and step forward to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room and face the microwave.
Heat the bread slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn right and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the bread slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Heat a bread slice and place it on the counter to the left of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter behind the faucet.
Turn left and walk to the white table.
Slice the loaf of bread on the table that is to the right of the tomato.
Turn around and walk back to the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the knife horizontally on the counter to the left of the sink, in front of the yellow apple.
Turn left and walk back to the table with the loaf of bread on it.
Take the second slice of bread from the right.
Turn around and take the slice of bread to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the slice of bread on the plate inside, then close the door. Set the timer for 2 seconds; once done heating, remove the slice of bread from the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the slice of bread standing on its edge perpendicular to the center of the knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of bread perpendicular to a knife on the counter to the left of the sink.
